    { "kind": 1, "languageId": "markdown", "value": "------", "output": [], "executionSummary": {} },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "## Part 4: Add a pop up window ",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "We'll add a pop up window to each marker to display additional information about the WindTurbine. We use the `WindTurbinePopup` component defined in <a href='../../ui/c3/src/components/WindTurbinePopup.tsx'>academyUI/ui/c3/src/components/WindTurbinePopup.tsx</a>.\n\nAdd the following import statement to <a href=\"../../ui/c3/src/customInstances/WindTurbine.HomePage.tsx\"><code>WindTurbine.HomePage.tsx</code></a>:",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 2,
      "languageId": "typescriptreact",
      "value": "/*\n  WindTurbine.HomePage.tsx\n*/\n// Other imports ...\nimport WindTurbinePopup from '@c3/app/ui/src/components/WindTurbinePopup';",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "To populate `WindTurbinePopup`, we pass in the WindTurbine object as a prop as we loop through the list of turbines.\n\nAdd the `<WindTurbinePopup>` component to the markers, like in the following cell:",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 2,
      "languageId": "typescriptreact",
      "value": "/*\n  WindTurbine.HomePage.tsx\n*/\n\n//return (\n// <>\n//   ...\n//  {/* Wind Turbine Markers */}\n//  {(turbines).map((turbine) => (\n//    <Marker \n//      key={turbine.id} \n//      position={[turbine.latitude, turbine.longitude]} \n//      icon={windTurbineIcon}\n//      {...{} as any}>\n          <WindTurbinePopup turbine={turbine} />\n//  </Marker>\n// ))}",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    { "kind": 1, "languageId": "markdown", "value": "### Verify result", "output": [], "executionSummary": {} },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "Refresh your UI. When you click on a marker on the map, you should see a popup window with the turbine details.\n\n<img src=\"../../src/doc/img/lesson-4/popup.png\" width=\"800px\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    { "kind": 1, "languageId": "markdown", "value": "-----", "output": [], "executionSummary": {} },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "### Summary\nYou saved fetched turbines to React state and plotted markers with popups on the map, establishing the visual representation of turbine data.\n\n<style>\n    .c3-a-alert {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      padding: 16px 20px;\n      align-self: stretch;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      border: 1px solid;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-style: normal;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      line-height: 150%;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      width: auto;\n    }\n\n    .c3-a-alert-warning {\n      background-color: rgb(178,235,242);\n      border-color: rgb(0,96,100);\n      color: rgba(17, 17, 18, 0.95);\n    }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"c3-a-alert c3-a-alert-warning\">\n    <p>Congratulations! You completed the hands-on lessons in the UI Framework Fundamentals course. <strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Remember to complete the <a href=\"https://learn.c3.ai/ui-framework-fundamentals/410413\" style=\"color: blue;\">quiz</a> before continuing to the next course in the learning path.</strong></p>\n</div>",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "<div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; margin-top:24px; align-items:center; width:100%;\">\n  <a href=\"./03-fetch-turbine-data.c3nb\"\n     aria-label=\"Go to Lesson 2: Fetch Turbine Data\"\n     style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; border:1px solid #d0d7de; background:#f6f8fa; color:#0b1026; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;\">\n    ← Previous: Fetch Turbine Data\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"../redux-actions-and-reducers/05-create-map-filter.c3nb\"\n     aria-label=\"Go to Lesson 4: Create Map Filter\"\n     style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; border:1px solid #1f6feb; background:#1f6feb; color:#ffffff; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;\">\n    Next: Create Map Filter →\n  </a>\n</div>",
